            <description><![CDATA[<h1>Dictate Anywhere 2.2.2</h1>
<ul>
<li>Added a quick-access Custom Vocabulary panel from the menu bar for fast word entry.</li>
<li>Removed the Cmd+C keyboard shortcut from the Copy Last Transcript menu item to avoid conflicts.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
