            <description><![CDATA[<h1>Dictate Anywhere 2.2.1</h1>
<ul>
<li>Refined the dictation overlay UI with a more polished pill layout and status presentation.</li>
<li>Improved the listening overlay behavior for live transcript preview and waveform display.</li>
<li>Polished overlay transitions and sizing across listening, processing, success, and clipboard-only states.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
